[SPEAKER_00] ili stvari ne mozak, um, turbulentan.

3455
01:35:23,479 --> 01:35:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] Mora da ga smiriš.

3456
01:35:25,340 --> 01:35:27,819
[SPEAKER_00] Da li će njega da smiriš kroz meditaciju,

3457
01:35:27,819 --> 01:35:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] kroz tišinu,

3458
01:35:29,220 --> 01:35:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] kroz boravak u prirodi,

3459
01:35:30,699 --> 01:35:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] kroz molitvu, meni je totalno nebitno.

3460
01:35:33,199 --> 01:35:34,840
[SPEAKER_00] Smiri mozak,

3461
01:35:34,840 --> 01:35:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] jasnoće će se pojaviti.

3462
01:35:36,619 --> 01:35:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kada je, ako ode mu sam na more,

3463
01:35:39,260 --> 01:35:40,939
[SPEAKER_00] ako talasi, roka i cepaju,

3464
01:35:40,939 --> 01:35:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] oluje ti ne vidiš ništa,

3465
01:35:42,420 --> 01:35:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali kada je more, mirno vidiš daleko.

3466
01:35:44,380 --> 01:35:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] E tako je isto i ovdje.

3467
01:35:46,619 --> 01:35:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] Mora sebe daš vremena

3468
01:35:48,840 --> 01:35:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] da umiriš svoj um.

3469
01:35:51,180 --> 01:35:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] A um se umiruje stvarno lako šetnjom,

3470
01:35:53,279 --> 01:35:54,520
[SPEAKER_00] morakom u prirodi,

3471
01:35:54,520 --> 01:35:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] tišinom,

3472
01:35:55,380 --> 01:35:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] meditacijom,

3473
01:35:56,760 --> 01:35:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] molitvom,

3474
01:35:57,840 --> 01:35:59,560
[SPEAKER_00] pisanjem

3475
01:35:59,560 --> 01:36:00,899
[SPEAKER_00] i doćeti.

3476
01:36:00,960 --> 01:36:01,439
[SPEAKER_00] pjevanjem,

3477
01:36:01,439 --> 01:36:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] plesanjem,

3478
01:36:02,420 --> 01:36:03,060
[SPEAKER_00] plesanjem,

3479
01:36:03,060 --> 01:36:03,439
[SPEAKER_00] bravo,

3480
01:36:03,439 --> 01:36:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] dinamična meditacija.

3481
01:36:05,180 --> 01:36:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] i kada dođe,

3482
01:36:06,140 --> 01:36:08,800
[SPEAKER_00] neka ta jebena odluka

3483
01:36:08,800 --> 01:36:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] bude sa tako jasnom namjerom

3484
01:36:11,260 --> 01:36:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] da će spaliti sve brodove

3485
01:36:13,359 --> 01:36:15,140
[SPEAKER_00] i da nema nazad.

3486
01:36:15,140 --> 01:36:16,939
[SPEAKER_00] I to je sve.

3487
01:36:16,939 --> 01:36:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kad završi se moja radionica

3488
01:36:18,819 --> 01:36:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] od 12 sati,

3489
01:36:19,739 --> 01:36:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem,

3490
01:36:20,300 --> 01:36:20,520
[SPEAKER_00] eh,

3491
01:36:20,520 --> 01:36:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] sad ste sve čuli,

3492
01:36:22,340 --> 01:36:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] naučili,

3493
01:36:23,239 --> 01:36:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali da li znate od čega

3494
01:36:24,680 --> 01:36:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] zaista zavisi vaša promjena?

3495
01:36:27,039 --> 01:36:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] I oni sad očekuju nešto spektaklno,

3496
01:36:28,960 --> 01:36:29,479
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem.

3497
01:36:30,100 --> 01:36:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Samo od jedne stvari,

3498
01:36:31,460 --> 01:36:32,100
[SPEAKER_00] točno dve.

3499
01:36:32,100 --> 01:36:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] Prva je

3500
01:36:33,359 --> 01:36:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] od vaše sposobnosti

3501
01:36:34,960 --> 01:36:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] da zadržite fokus

3502
01:36:36,100 --> 01:36:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljno dugo

3503
01:36:36,680 --> 01:36:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] ka tom cilju

3504
01:36:37,680 --> 01:36:39,479
[SPEAKER_00] i druga stvar je

3505
01:36:39,479 --> 01:36:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] od vaše konstantnog dijaloga

3506
01:36:41,640 --> 01:36:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojim umom.

3507
01:36:42,880 --> 01:36:44,600
[SPEAKER_00] Kako sebi pričaš

3508
01:36:44,600 --> 01:36:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad je dobro,

3509
01:36:45,340 --> 01:36:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali kako sebi pričaš

3510
01:36:47,279 --> 01:36:48,140
[SPEAKER_00] kad nije dobro

3511
01:36:48,140 --> 01:36:48,979
[SPEAKER_00] što je još važnije.

3512
01:36:48,979 --> 01:36:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

3513
01:36:49,600 --> 01:36:50,600
[SPEAKER_00] toga zavisi.

3514
01:36:50,600 --> 01:36:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] I to su neke stvari

3515
01:36:52,760 --> 01:36:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] koje,

3516
01:36:53,039 --> 01:36:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] Bob Proktor je savršeno,

3517
01:36:54,159 --> 01:36:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

3518
01:36:54,380 --> 01:36:55,060
[SPEAKER_00] to je u pravu

3519
01:36:55,060 --> 01:36:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] i nije ti potrebno

3520
01:36:57,380 --> 01:36:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] ništa od ovog stvari.

3521
01:36:58,220 --> 01:36:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ja,

3522
01:36:58,699 --> 01:36:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ti nije potrebno?

3523
01:36:59,779 --> 01:37:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer opet,

3524
01:37:00,220 --> 01:37:02,479
[SPEAKER_00] tvoj mozak uči

3525
01:37:02,479 --> 01:37:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] kroz iskustvo

3526
01:37:03,260 --> 01:37:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] i ti samo modifikuješ stvari

3527
01:37:04,760 --> 01:37:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] i tvoja žena to naučila

3528
01:37:06,119 --> 01:37:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] na intuitivni način,

3529
01:37:06,819 --> 01:37:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji način.

3530
01:37:07,579 --> 01:37:08,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tvoja žena kada bi htjela,

3531
01:37:08,800 --> 01:37:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] ona ne bi znala

3532
01:37:10,159 --> 01:37:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] da to intelektualizuje

3533
01:37:11,699 --> 01:37:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] na neki način

3534
01:37:12,380 --> 01:37:13,439
[SPEAKER_00] ko možda mi to radimo,

3535
01:37:13,439 --> 01:37:14,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali bi ti rekla

3536
01:37:14,680 --> 01:37:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što si ti sad rekao.

3537
01:37:15,619 --> 01:37:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta?

3538
